          <title>Chicago Blackhawks fire Luke Richardson, IceHogs' Sorensen named interim head coach</title>
          <description><![CDATA[CHICAGO (WGN) — Chicago Blackhawks General Manager Kyle Davidson announced Thursday the team has fired head coach Luke Richardson. Rockford IceHogs head coach Anders Sorensen has been named interim head coach and will assume duties immediately.]]></description>
